137
00:11:20.791 --> 00:11:22.833  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Evliyim, iki de kızım var.

138
00:11:23.250 --> 00:11:25.083  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Allah bağışlasın.

139
00:11:25.625 --> 00:11:28.958  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Benim de altı tane oğlum var.

140
00:11:29.041 --> 00:11:31.375  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
