167
00:12:42.416 --> 00:12:44.416  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Ahırdan hiç mektep olur mu?

168
00:12:44.583 --> 00:12:46.666  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Mektebi devlet yapacak.

169
00:12:47.500 --> 00:12:49.583  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Yarın ola, hayrola muhtar.

170
00:12:50.166 --> 00:12:51.125  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Muallim Bey,

171
00:12:51.416 --> 00:12:53.958  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
valla sen geldin, keyfim yerinde.

172
00:12:54.875 --> 00:12:57.333  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Lakin, çok yerine geldi.

173
00:12:59.750 --> 00:13:04.583  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Yarın bütün bekârlar dışarıda hazır olsun.

174
00:13:07.916 --> 00:13:09.333  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[sesi titreyerek] Allah razı olsun baba.

175
00:13:11.208 --> 00:13:12.083  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[muallim] Allah'ım,

