00:15:38.041 --> 00:15:39.500  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Aziz.

196
00:15:42.250 --> 00:15:43.708  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
