221
00:17:00.833 --> 00:17:03.375  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Celal, bak beni kızdırma.

222
00:17:03.458 --> 00:17:05.208  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Yav sen önce kendi tipine,

223
00:17:05.291 --> 00:17:07.208  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
