233
00:17:35.416 --> 00:17:36.625  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Celal.

234
00:17:36.833 --> 00:17:40.625  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
