254
00:18:57.500 --> 00:19:00.708  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Kızım, geç otur hele şöyle.

255
00:19:05.750 --> 00:19:07.416  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
