567
00:45:37.916 --> 00:45:40.666  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Gazi Mustafa Kemal Atatürk

568
00:45:40.750 --> 00:45:42.583  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
ve şehitlerimiz

569
