ve de ebediyete intikal etmiş

570
00:45:46.375 --> 00:45:48.500  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
kıymetli muallimlerimiz için

571
00:45:48.583 --> 00:45:51.250  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
hepinizi bir dakika

572
00:45:51.333 --> 00:45:53.583  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
saygı duruşuna davet ediyorum.

573
00:45:55.166 --> 00:45:56.625  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[mırıldanmalar]

574
00:45:59.166 --> 00:46:01.208  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
