00:46:17.208 --> 00:46:18.958  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Vallahi Celal doğru söylüyor.

582
00:46:19.375 --> 00:46:20.916  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Tamam.

583
00:46:21.000 --> 00:46:23.708  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Sayın Haydar Bey ve Sayın Muhtar,

584
00:46:23.791 --> 00:46:26.250  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
sizleri kurdele kesmeye davet ediyorum.

585
00:46:26.333 --> 00:46:27.583  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Açılış yapacağız.

586
00:46:35.375 --> 00:46:36.583  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Muhtar Bey.

587
00:46:40.000 --> 00:46:43.708  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Evet arkadaşlar,
