588
00:46:46.875 --> 00:46:49.375  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Şimdi durun. Çocuklar,

589
00:46:49.458 --> 00:46:51.708  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
hadi bakayım ders yapacağız. Girin içeri.

590
00:47:01.250 --> 00:47:04.000  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Gir bakayım, sıra ver, yavaş.

591
00:47:05.541 --> 00:47:09.875  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Muhtar, sen gel bak bakayım. Gel.

592
00:47:10.958 --> 00:47:12.458  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Buyurun.

593
00:47:12.958 --> 00:47:14.916  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[muhtar] Çok güzel olmuş, hayırlı olsun.

594
00:47:15.708 --> 00:47:17.208  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Aziz'in sesleri]

595
00:47:24.958 --> 00:47:26.250  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Her şey için sağ olun.

596
00:47:26.333 --> 00:47:27.583  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[muhtar] Hadi Haydar.

597
00:47:31.583 --> 00:47:33.083  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Hişt!

598
00:47:33.625 --> 00:47:36.250  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Hadi bakayım, oturun yerlerinize.

599
00:47:38.625 --> 00:47:39.500  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Güzel.

600
00:47:40.750 --> 00:47:45.250  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Sen ne yapıyorsun burada?
