601
00:47:49.791 --> 00:47:54.083  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Evet çocuklar, bugün ilk ders günümüz.

602
00:47:54.791 --> 00:47:56.916  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Derse başlamadan önce,

603
00:47:57.416 --> 00:48:00.541  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
şunu söyleyeceğim.
Ben sizin öğretmeninizim.

604
00:48:01.458 --> 00:48:06.208  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Ben ismim Mahir, soyadım da Yılmaz.

605
00:48:12.958 --> 00:48:15.291  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Bunu sen bana vermiştin, hatırladın mı?

606
00:48:19.875 --> 00:48:20.833  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Senin adın ne?

607
00:48:23.208 --> 00:48:24.458  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Arkadaşının adı ne?

608
00:48:24.583 --> 00:48:26.250  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
O, Cemilo'nun oğlu deriz.

609
00:48:26.333 --> 00:48:28.166  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
İsmi Gaffur.

610
00:48:30.583 --> 00:48:31.708  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Gaffur ha?

611
00:48:44.208 --> 00:48:47.875  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Aziz seslenir]

612
00:48:50.291 --> 00:48:54.625  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gök gürültüsü]

613
00:48:54.708 --> 00:48:56.000  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
İyi akşamlar Mehmet Ali.

614
00:48:56.083 --> 00:48:57.541  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
İyi akşamlar.

615
00:49:26.541 --> 00:49:29.208  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[yağmur sesi]

616
00:49:31.791 --> 00:49:33.583  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Adil Usta, hoş geldiniz?

