621
00:49:45.000 --> 00:49:47.666  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
İstersen gel. Hasta olacaksın.

622
00:49:49.416 --> 00:49:53.416  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Aziz bağırır]

