00:50:21.208 --> 00:50:22.583  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Oturun biraz. Sohbet edelim.

624
00:50:22.666 --> 00:50:23.791  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Estağfurullah.

625
00:50:27.583 --> 00:50:29.416  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Hoş geldiniz.
-Hoş bulduk.

626
00:50:29.875 --> 00:50:30.958  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Ee, Celal.

627
00:50:31.791 --> 00:50:32.958  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Evlilik nasıl gidiyor?

628
00:50:33.083 --> 00:50:33.916  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[utanarak] İyi.

629
00:50:34.125 --> 00:50:36.291  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
