00:50:59.666 --> 00:51:02.250  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Ben tahsilimi ilçede tamamladım.

637
00:51:02.333 --> 00:51:04.458  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
