638
00:51:07.625 --> 00:51:08.958  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[güler] Cahil.

639
00:51:10.333 --> 00:51:12.083  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Benim çok asi bir yapım,

640
00:51:12.208 --> 00:51:13.833  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
