648
00:51:36.416 --> 00:51:38.000  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Cemilo dağa neden çıktı?

649
00:51:39.416 --> 00:51:41.291  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
