00:52:55.750 --> 00:52:57.208  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
İnsan hiç böyle yapar mı?

665
00:52:57.541 --> 00:53:00.166  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
